c: 3
v: 153
t: "Yabonani nina nabaleka ninganyeki nokunyeka, waba uMthunywa engemva kwenu, enikhwaza ukuba nibuye. Apho uAllâh Waninika unxunguphalo emva konxunguphalo ngendlela yembuyekezo, Enifundisa ukuba ningabi buhlungu ngoko kuniphosileyo, nangoko kunihleleyo. UAllâh Ukwazi konke oko nikwenzayo"